<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[١٦]</span> بَابٌ التَّوْقِيتُ فِي حَلْقِ الْعَانَةِ وَنَتْفِ الْإِبِطِ وَأَخْذِ الشَّارِبِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٦٠-<span class="c5"> أَخْبَرَنِي سُلَيْمَانُ بْنُ الْأَشْعَثِ قَالَ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">سَمِعْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ يُسْأَلُ:</span> <span class="c4">[فِي]</span> كَمْ تُحلْقُ الْعَانَةُ؟<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> قَالُوا فِي أَرْبَعِينَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>